# Option

```scala
val some: Option[Int] = Some(42)
val none: Option[Int] = None
println(some.isDefined)
println(none.isDefined)
println(some.isEmpty)
println(none.isEmpty)
println(some.getOrElse(0))
println(none.getOrElse(99))
println(some.map(_ * 2).getOrElse(0))
println(none.map(_ * 2).getOrElse(0))
val xs = List(Some(1), None, Some(3), None, Some(5))
println(xs.filter(_.isDefined).map(_.getOrElse(0)).mkString(", "))
```
